title: Fred Upton
added: Upton won reelection with 55.89% of the vote against Democratic candidate Jon Hoadley (40.19%), Libertarian Party candidate Jeff Depoy (2.75%), and Green Party candidate John Lawrence (1.17%). <ref>;2018 election
